 up to the raid leader.  If you are concerned, ask and make your points to him/her before the raid starts.  My persnal opinion is that need before greed should always pervail, and casters cant get near the full benefit of this piece.  There are cheaper belts with more wis for sure and probably the same with int, tho i cant think of any off the top of my head.  If all the tanks had better haste items, then it would be no problem for casters to roll but as i said, i frequently see 60s using fbss so that isnt likely...<br><br>I'll Shut up now<br>&nbsp;<br>Ok, I'll shut up now.<br><br>Slein Jinn &lt;Honor Knights&gt;<br>Dread Knight of Innoruuk<br>Everyone's least favorite server, E'ci</td></tr>
